"{\"uid\": \"nbclosangeles.com-paris-2024-summer-olympics-olympians-wearing-glasses-inspire-young-athletes-3483571\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Olympians wearing glasses are inspiring young athletes, including a 17-year-old gymnast in Huntington Beach, who also wears glasses.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 132, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 91, \"end\": 107, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huntington_Beach,_California\", \"score\": 0.9999999939884674, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Huntington Beach\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huntington_Beach,_California\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huntington_Beach,_California\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hetty Cheng reports for the NBC4 News at 5 p.m., Thursday, August 8, 2024.\", \"from\": 133, \"to\": 207, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 161, \"end\": 165, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KNBC\", \"score\": 0.9985007751078917, \"rank\": 0.0015014759421780502, \"text\": \"NBC4\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KNBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KNBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A young gymnast from Rancho Santa Margarita has become more proud of his not-so-perfect vision after seeing USA Men's Gymnastics Olympian Stephen Nedoroscik sporting his glasses before performing hisviral pommel horseroutine.\", \"from\": 209, \"to\": 434, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 230, \"end\": 252, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rancho_Santa_Margarita\", \"score\": 0.9999999994777227, \"rank\": 5.223448460403047e-10, \"text\": \"Rancho Santa Margarita\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rancho_Santa_Margarita\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rancho_Santa_Margarita\"}, {\"begin\": 317, \"end\": 320, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9956590221725714, \"rank\": 0.004315475795458334, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 327, \"end\": 337, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gymnastics\", \"score\": 0.617103132413483, \"rank\": 0.6204441588207257, \"text\": \"Gymnastics\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gymnastics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gymnastics\"}, {\"begin\": 347, \"end\": 365, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_Nedoroscik\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stephen Nedoroscik\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_Nedoroscik\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_Nedoroscik\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stephen Nedoroscik became an overnight sensation when he propelled his team to a bronze medal in the men's gymnastics all-around team event and earned another bronze in the pommel horse.\", \"from\": 436, \"to\": 622, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 436, \"end\": 454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_Nedoroscik\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stephen Nedoroscik\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_Nedoroscik\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_Nedoroscik\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just prior to starting his routine, he carefully removed his glasses and set them aside.\", \"from\": 623, \"to\": 711, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Stream Los Angeles News for free, 24/7, wherever you are.\", \"from\": 713, \"to\": 770, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 720, \"end\": 731, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999459664665, \"rank\": 5.393100825839315e-08, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When his glasses came off, his skills turned on.\", \"from\": 772, \"to\": 820, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"17-year-old gymnast Noah Tung saw himself in Nedoroscik as he wore glasses and they are both experts on the pommel horse.\", \"from\": 822, \"to\": 943, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 842, \"end\": 846, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\", \"score\": 0.80936524323218, \"rank\": 0.23218094814024173, \"text\": \"Noah\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think it's hilarious.\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 969, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I love the attention he's getting - I think he deserves it,\\\" Tung said.\", \"from\": 970, \"to\": 1041, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tung, who started gymnastics at 5 years old, began following Nedoroscik's Olympic journey about a year ago.\", \"from\": 1043, \"to\": 1150, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I feel like I was competing.\", \"from\": 1152, \"to\": 1181, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I felt like Stephen,\\\" the Rancho Santa Margarita teen added.\", \"from\": 1182, \"to\": 1242, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The similarities do not stop with the sport and the spectacles: Tung is also a Rubik's Cube enthusiast like his pommel horse hero.\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1376, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He says this helps him with the analytical part of gymnastics.\", \"from\": 1377, \"to\": 1439, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just love all the ways you can analyze your routines and almost every single detail in your training comes into not only your daily life - but your routine in general,\\\" he explained.\", \"from\": 1441, \"to\": 1626, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tung says he just started wearing contacts while competing a few weeks ago, so he's used to depending on his sense of touch.\", \"from\": 1628, \"to\": 1752, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nedoroscik has described doing the same.\", \"from\": 1753, \"to\": 1793, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tung added that he's also been inspired by other Olympians, like Brazilian gold medalist Rebeca Andrade, who has to put on her glasses to see the scoreboard.\", \"from\": 1795, \"to\": 1952, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1884, \"end\": 1898, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebeca_Andrade\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rebeca Andrade\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebeca_Andrade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebeca_Andrade\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think it's great - Stephen has been such an awesome ambassador in this sport.\", \"from\": 1954, \"to\": 2034, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think it's cool for these younger athletes to see somebody - who is very much so into their own things outside of gymnasts as well,\\\" CEO of Scats Gymnastics Dave Peters said, referring to Nedoroscik's love of the Rubik's Cube.\", \"from\": 2035, \"to\": 2263, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2177, \"end\": 2182, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney_Coordinated_Adaptive_Traffic_System\", \"score\": 0.9999994023207331, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Scats\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney_Coordinated_Adaptive_Traffic_System\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney_Coordinated_Adaptive_Traffic_System\"}, {\"begin\": 2183, \"end\": 2193, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gymnastics\", \"score\": 0.617103132413483, \"rank\": 0.6204441588207257, \"text\": \"Gymnastics\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gymnastics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gymnastics\"}, {\"begin\": 2194, \"end\": 2205, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dave_Peters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dave Peters\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dave_Peters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dave_Peters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As for Tung's vision for the future: he has his eyes on the 2028 Los Angeles Olympics.\", \"from\": 2265, \"to\": 2351, \"entities\": []}]}"